{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6aed2c84d7","title":"关于在公私合营企业中进行肃反工作的意见","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ade942fc7a","index":0,"year":1957,"month":1,"day":5,"articleId":"6aed2c84d7"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji37","name":"毛泽东全集第37卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/37-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji37":{"comments":[{"id":"1a0bda9441","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6aed2c84d7","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"本篇一是毛泽东审阅中共中央转发天津市委关于1957年肃反规划的批语稿时，对增写一条所作的说明；本篇二是毛泽东在中央批语稿中增写的第三条。"},{"id":"620b89cff3","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6aed2c84d7","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈叔通，当时任中华全国工商业联合会主任委员、全国人大常委会副委员长、政协全国委员会副主席。荣毅仁，当时任中华全国工商业联合会副主任委员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"eadceb2225","type":"title","text":"关于在公私合营企业中进行肃反工作的意见“","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6aed2c84d7"},{"id":"1a0bda9441","type":"paragraph","text":"增加一条，这是在中央会议上谈过的，并已向陈叔通、荣毅仁回及各省市资本家代表宣布过","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6aed2c84d7"},{"id":"620b89cff3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6aed2c84d7"},{"id":"84404458c3","type":"paragraph","text":"一月五日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6aed2c84d7"},{"id":"ac95b720e3","type":"paragraph","text":"关于在公私合营企业中进行肃反工作的问题，不但应吸收那些自愿参加的资方人员参加，而且应和工商联及民建会协商，取得他们同意，方可进行。对于资方人员中查出的反革命分子，在结案时也要有工商联民建会参加审查，得其同意，方可结案。各省市目前是否在私方人员中进行肃反，由各省市自己决定。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6aed2c84d7"}],"page":{"id":"37a08d7852","publicationId":"maoquanji37","articleId":"6aed2c84d7","start":220,"end":221}}}},"__N_SSG":true}